To see how the protocol works, see the PROTOCOL file.

For informations on library usage, run doxygen and see the doc/ directory.

To compile and install the library, do:

-------------------------
./bootstrap

./configure 

make

make install
-------------------------

You will require gcc (obviously), automake/autoconf, libtool, and dev. versions of openssl, libmhash, and zlib. You will require doxygen to generate the documentation.

